Package io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDBConfiguration
    An interface for MongoDB configurations
    IDBCredentials
    Login credentials for a MongoDB
    IDBLoadingTask
    An interface for a data loading task in MongoDB.
    IEntityMapper
    A mapper which can map MongoDB entries to labelled data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DBDriver
    A driver for creating new connections to a MongoDB.
    DefaultEntityMapper
    A default mapper for MongoDB entries.
    LemmaEntityMapper
    Same behaviour as DefaultEntityMapper but lemmatize the given features.
    MongoConstants
    String constants for the entity mapping.
    MongoLoadingPipe
    A pipe which takes a loading task as input and then push read entities (mapped as labelled entities).
